{
  "stem": "11998.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, of course, the, the, the first thing that happened immediately the first-- almost the first day of the war, Lodz was bombed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the 1st of September or 2nd of September.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of '39.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- most of the bombs were incendiary bombs so that a lot of the buildings became infernos.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to sit for hours in bunkers and basements while the buildings were shaking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we never knew whether there was going to be a direct hit or not.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The sounds, you know, were, were terrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as an 11-year-old child, I was very much affected by it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then it didn't take very long when the, when the Nazis occupied.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the first encounter, you know-- first, when they marched in, we all ran into the streets to see this [INAUDIBLE] to this fantastic army march in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were very impressive with the shining boots and shining tanks and armored carriers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were fascinated to see them come through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a real war machinery.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And only about two or three days later-- we lived in a courtyard-- and they came in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they went into the shtiebel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they got all the Jews out from their prayer with their prayer shawls on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you know, if it was during the week, they most likely had their-- they did have their tefillin on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were starting to come and photograph these archaic people and make fun.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They would shave their-- they would cut their beards off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They would--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would take them in and ask them to take the [? talesim ?] and, and dance on them, and all the time with guns pointing at them and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] camera crews filming it.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
